description: Hafthor Bjornsson, who was Ser Gregor "The Mountain" Clegane in the series, lifted 501kg.
title: Hafthor Bjornsson: Game of Thrones actor breaks 501kg deadlift record
title_page: Hafthor Bjornsson: Game of Thrones actor breaks 501kg deadlift record - BBC News
maintext: "It's great - there's nothing better than proving people wrong. So many people didn't believe in me, so many people that said, '501kg is never going to go up'... But I also had a lot of support."
